{
  "texts": [
    "The triplet neural-network maps the fused representation to predict the confidence scores of protein GO terms.",
    "The ATGO+ method is a combination of the ATGO method and a sequence homology-based method, resulting in superior performance compared to ATGO.",
    "CLEAN has been developed based on the contrastive learning for predictive assignments of EC numbers to enzymes 46.",
    "The CLEAN method learns embedded representations of enzymes, in which proteins of the same EC numbers are close to each in Euclidean distances; otherwise, they are far from each other.",
    "The positive and negative samples are defined by the distances to the anchor sequence."
  ]
}